| ----- | --- | --------- |
| (2,2) | 4   | ✅         |
| (2,1) | 3   | ❌         |
| (2,7) | 9   | ❌         |
| (2,1) | 3   | ❌         |
| (2,7) | 9   | ❌         |
| (1,7) | 8   | ✅         |

Answer

```text
2
```

